 mods vs. Will','9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP','0 (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)\\nMedium (+6; LoS)','Instantaneous (+0)\\nConcentration (+4)','Conical burst; 2 sq (+0), 4 sq (+2)\\nSpherical spread; 2 sq rad (+2), 4 sq rad (+4), 6 sq rad (+8)','You create a pattern of vivid and clashing colors that affects the minds of creatures within.','Hypnotism option: Instead of suffering the stunning/blinding/unconsciousness effect described below, affected creatures become fascinated by the pattern and do nothing but stare at it, unless they are attacked.\\nMobility option (req concentration duration): You can move the pattern 6 squares per round (no AP cost). If you use the hypnotism option, affected creatures will try to follow the pattern. If the pattern leads creatures into obvious danger, you must succeed on a second check against their Will.','S - The target is stunned for 1 round.\\nES - The target is stunned for 1 round and blinded the rest of the encounter.\\nCS - The target is rendered unconscious for the rest of the encounter.\\nF - The target is unaffected.',NULL),(37,'Command Creature','[Su, MR, AoO, Mind, Lang, Charm]','Divine - Charm\\nPsi - Telepathy','d20 + Cha mod + Body & Mind skill mod + MAM + AB + other mods vs. Will','9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)','1 PP','Close (+0; LoS)\\nMedium (+3; LoS)','Special (+0)','1 creature (+0)\\n2 creatures (+2)\\n3-4 creatures (+4)\\n5-8 creatures (+6)\\n9-16 creatures (+8)','You give the targets one of the following commands, and they will obey it to the best of their abilities for the spell\'s duration.\\nApproach - The affected targets move toward you as quickly and directly as possible.\\nDrop - The affected targets drop anything held in their hands.\\nFall - The affected targets drop to the ground and remain prone.\\nFlee - The affected targets move away from you as quickly as possible.\\nHalt - The affected targets stand in place and take no actions.',NULL,'S - The target obeys your command for 1 round.\\nCS - The effect\'s duration increases to one encounter.\\nF - The target ignores the command.',NULL),(38,'Commune with Nature','[Su, AoO]','Divine - Insight and Nature',NULL,'10 min (+0)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','9 PP\\n+4 PP for full commune','Personal (+0)','Instantaneous (+0)','You (+0)','The basic spell reveals three of the following facts: ground and terrain, plants present, minerals present, bodies of water, people present, population of animals and monstrous animals, unnatural creatures present, general state of the environment, and presence of buildings.\\nIn outdoor settings, the radius of the spell is 1 km per skill level, and in natural underground settings, the radius is 25 m per skill level. No information is gained about the insides of buildings, cities, dungeons, etc.\\nBy paying the extra cost for a full commune, you gain all of the information listed above (instead of just three facts).','Stone tell option: You gain additional information from natural or worked stone in the area, including who or what has touched or walked on it, what is covered or concealed by it, etc.',NULL,NULL),(39,'Comprehend Languages','[Su, MR, AoO]','Arcane - Divination\\nDivine - Insight\\nPsi - Telepathy',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP per language\\n+2 PP for speech','Personal or Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','You (+0)\\n1 creature (+2)\\n2 creatures (+4)\\n3-4 creatures (+6)\\n5-8 creatures (+8)\\n9-16 creatures (+10)','The target becomes able to understand the spoken or written words of one or more languages. You do not have to identify or name the language - hearing or seeing the language is enough.\\nUnder most circumstances, it is possible to read and understand one page (250 words) per minute.\\nMagically hidden or encrypted writing may require an opposed skill check.\\nIf you pay the extra cost for speech, target also becomes able to speak and write all of the chosen languages.','Speech option: The target also becomes able to speak and write all of the chosen languages.\\nAnimal speech option (req Divine - Animals): The target becomes able to understand and communicate with all normal and monstrous animals. Note, however, that this does not automatically alter the attitude of an animal.\\nPlant speech option (req Divine - Plants): The target becomes able to understand and communicate with all normal and monstrous plants. Note, however, that this does not automatically alter the attitude of a plant.',NULL,NULL),(40,'Consecrate','[Su, AoO]','Divine - Blessing and Protection',NULL,'1 h (+0)\\n10 min (+4)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)\\nM (holy water and silver)\\nF (divine focus)','1 PP','Tch (+0)','1 day (D; +0)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','Spherical emanation; 4 sq rad (+0), 6 sq rad (+2), 8 sq rad (+4)','Consecrates an area with divine energy. Attempts to turn or rebuke (depending on the deity) undead gain a +3 divine bonus within the area, and the opposite type of action receives a -3 divine penalty. In addition, all undead receive either a -1 penalty or +1 divine bonus on all attacks, damage rolls, and defenses. All of the above bonuses and penalties are doubled, if the area contains an altar or similar fixture of your deity.\\nThe material components cost 100 sp per PL.\\nCertain other spells can be cast as part of the consecration, either affecting all of the deity\'s followers or all of its enemies. This increases the PP cost by the cost of the other spell(s), and therefore also increases the cost of the material components.','Planar seal option: All planar summoning and travel into or within the area must beat the spell\'s PL.\\nForbiddance option [MR, Radiant or Necrotic]: Creatures that differ from the deity\'s alignment take damage when they try to enter the area. Make a +10 attack against Will (S - Those of opposed alignment take 12d6 HP of radiant or necrotic damage, and those of differing alignment take 6d6 HP; F - Half damage). The forbiddance can include a password that lets creatures enter freely, regardless of their alignment.',NULL,NULL),(41,'Contact Other Plane','[Su, AoO, Secret]','Arcane - Conjuration and Divination','Spellcasting check vs. DC','10 min (+0)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','9 PP','Personal (+0)','Concentration (+0)','You (+0)','You contact a powerful extraplanar entity in order to receive advice and information. The entity will provide one single-word answer per round and a maximum of one answer per 2 skill levels. The list below shows different planes, with PP modifier, DC modifier, chance of correct answer for each question, etc.\\nElemental: +0 PP, DC 22, 01-34 - Correct, 35-62 - Don\'t know, 63-83 - Lie, 84-100 - Random\\nEnergy: +1 PP, DC 23, 01-39 - Correct, 40-65 - Don\'t know, 66-86 - Lie, 87-100 - Random\\nAstral: +2 PP, DC 24, 01-44 - Correct, 45-67 - Don\'t know, 68-88 - Lie, 89-100 - Random\\nOuter, demi-: +3 PP, DC 25, 01-49 - Correct, 50-70 - Don\'t know, 71-91 - Lie, 92-100 - Random\\nOuter, lesser: +5 PP, DC 27, 01-60 - Correct, 61-75 - Don\'t know, 76-95 - Lie, 96-100 - Random\\nOuter, interm.: +7 PP, DC 29, 01-73 - Correct, 74-81 - Don\'t know, 82-98 - Lie, 99-100 - Random\\nOuter, greater: +9 PP, DC 31, 01-88 - Correct, 89-90 - Don\'t know, 91-99 - Lie, 100 - Random',NULL,'S - You successfully contact the entity and can ask questions.\\nF - You fail to get any answers.\\nOF - You suffer a mental blowback and take 2d6 points of Int and Cha damage.',NULL),(42,'Control Air','[Su, AoO, Air]','Arcane - Aeromancy\\nDivine - Elements\\nPsi - Psychokinesis\\nCleric Affinity - Storm Domain',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for +/-15 m/s\\n3 PP for +/-30 m/s','0 (+0)\\nClose (+3; PoE)\\nMedium (+6; PoE)\\nLong (+9; PoE)','1 r (+0)\\nEncounter (D; +2)\\nOngoing (+6; 1 PP/h)\\nPerm