re.\\nDelay poison option: Suppresses the effects of any poison for 1 day, regardless of whether the target already has poison in its system or is exposed to poison during the day.\\nNeutralize poison option: Instead of temporarily suppressing the effects of poison, it removes all poison from the target\'s system and also makes it immune to poison for 1 day.\\nCure blindness option: You cure blindness, whether it is natural or magical. Lost eyes are not restored.\\nCure deafness option: You cure deafness, whether it is natural or magical. Lost ears are not restored.\\nCure disease option: Cures all diseases (and kills all parasites) that the target is suffering from. Certain magical diseases may require you to beat the DC of the disease with your spellcasting check.\\nCure insanity option: Cures any insanity, natural or magical, that the target is suffering from.\\nMedium restoration option: Restores all ability damage. Also restores ability drain to one ability score.\\nGreater restoration option: Restores all ability damage and ability drain.\\nLife force option: Restores any levels and/or AP drained recently (up to 1 day per skill level).',NULL,NULL),(62,'Cure Fatigue','[Su, MR, AoO, Radiant]','Divine - Life\\nPsi - Psychometabolism (target you only)',NULL,'6 AP (+0)\\n3 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for 10 SP\\n+2 PP per additional 5 SP','Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Instantaneous (+0)','1 creature (+0)\\n2 creatures (+2)\\n3-4 creatures (+4)\\n5-8 creatures (+6)\\n9-16 creatures (+8)','You channel radiant energy into the target creature(s), using it to cure their fatigue. When this spell is cast on multiple targets, each target is cured of the same amount (up to its maximum).',NULL,NULL,NULL),(63,'Curse','[Su, MR, AoO]','Divine - Retribution','(Tch: d20 + Dex mod + Weapons - Natural skill mod + MAM + AB + others mods vs. DeC and then)\\nd20 + Wis mod + Body & Mind skill mod + MAM + AB + other mods vs. Will','9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V