rection up to 20 squares per round.\\nShapeable option: The shape and direction of the darkness can be controlled each round. For example, you can turn it into a cone (like a bullseye lantern) or shape the darkness itself into a vaguely humanoid figure.\\nDeep darkness option: The radius is 12 squares (instead of 4).\\nBlacklight option: You are yourself not affected by the spell\'s area of darkness.',NULL,NULL),(65,'Deflective Shield','[Su, MR, AoO]','Arcane - Abjuration\\nDivine - Protection\\nPsi - Psychokinesis (target you only)',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)\\nReaction (+10)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for +2 bonus\\n+4 PP per additional +1 (up to +6 total)\\n+2 PP for +4 extra bonus against ranged weapons','Personal or Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Encounter (D; +0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','You (+0)\\n1 creature (+2)\\n2 creatures (+4)\\n3-4 creatures (+6)\\n5-8 creatures (+8)\\n9-16 creatures (+10)','You protect the target with a shimmering shield that provides a deflection bonus to DeC. Maximum total deflection bonus is +6 (or +10 against ranged if that extra bonus is paid for).','Projectile protection option: The target gains an additional +4 deflection bonus against projectiles, thrown weapons, and other ranged weapon attacks.\\nShadow shield option (req Arcane - Illumination; [Dark]): The shield becomes shadowy and grants the target concealment. The target also gains a +2 circumstance bonus to defenses against [Light] and [Radiant] effects.',NULL,NULL),(66,'Detect Alignment','[Su, AoO]','Divine - Insight\\nPsi - Clairsentience',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP for one aspect\\n+1 PP for fast detection\\n+4 PP for all aspects','0 (+0)','Concentration (+0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','Conical emanation; 12 sq (+0), 24 sq (+2), 50 sq (+4), 100 sq (+6)','You detect the presence of one particular alignment aspect (good, evil, law, or chaos), chosen at the time of casting. Typically, only strongly aligned creatures (e.g. most outsiders, clerics, templars) will be detectable.\\nFast detection: A single scan gives all the information (see below).\\nAll aspects: You detect all four alignment aspects at the same time.','Fast detection option: A single scan gives all the information (see below).\\nAll aspects option: You detect all four alignment aspects at the same time.','1st round - You detect the presence or absence of the chosen alignment aspect.\\n2nd round - You detect the number of auras of the chosen aspect.\\n3rd round - You detect the location and approximate strength of each aura.',NULL),(67,'Detect Life','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Divination and Necromancy\\nDivine - Insight and (Life or Death)',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP\\n+1 PP for fast detection','0 (+0)','Concentration (+0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','Conical emanation; 6 sq (+0), 9 sq (+2)','You detect life force.\\nFast detection: A single scan gives all the information (see below).','Fast detection option: A single scan gives all the information (see below).','1st round - You detect the presence or absence of living and undead creatures (but not constructs).\\n2nd round - You detect the number of living/undead creatures.\\n3rd round - You detect the location and status (healthy, bloodied, dying, or undead) of each aura.',NULL),(68,'Detect Magic','[Su, AoO]','Arcane - Divination\\nDivine - Insight\\nPsi - Clairsentience',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','1 PP\\n+1 PP for fast detection','0 (+0)','Concentration (+0)\\nOngoing (+4; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +8; 100 XP cost per PL)','Conical emanation; 12 sq (+0), 24 sq (+1)','You detect magical auras.\\nFast detection: A single scan gives all the information (see below).','Fast detection option: A single scan gives all the information (see below).\\nPoten