usory duplicate in your space. You can direct the duplicate to move anywhere within line of sight (with your own base speed and movement abilities). The duplicate is immune to all attacks.\\nProjection option: You create a single quasi-real duplicate of yourself within 40 squares. It looks, sounds, and smells like you but is intangible and immune to attacks. The duplicate mimics your actions (and speech) every round, unless you spend 5 AP to mentally direct it to act differently. You can choose to see and hear through the duplicate\'s senses, and you can switch your perception back and forth at no cost. You can cast your spells and use other supernatural powers through the projection, causing them to originate from (and even affect) the duplicate. If the distance between you and the duplicate exceeds 40 squares, or if you lose line of effect, the duplicate disappears instantly, and the spell ends.',NULL,NULL),(120,'Illusory Terrain','[Su, AoO, Illusion]','Arcane - Illusion',NULL,'10 min (+0)\\n1 min (+4)\\n1 r (+10)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)','5 PP','Medium (+0; PoE)\\nLong (+3; PoE)','Ongoing (+0; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +4)','200 x level cubes (S; +0)','The basic spell makes any natural terrain look, sound, smell, and feel like some other natural terrain. It cannot be used to hide or change creatures, equipment, and constructions.','Wall option: By spending additional PP you can create a visual illusion of natural or constructed walls, floors, and/or ceilings. Such illusions can also be used to hide real doors, pits, and openings.\\nIllusory construction option: You can also hide or change buildings and other constructions in the area.',NULL,NULL),(121,'Illusory Trap','[Su, AoO, Illusion]','Arcane - Illusion',NULL,'9 AP (+0)\\n6 AP (+6)','V (+0), Silent (+2)\\nS (+0), Still (+2)\\nM (50 sp of iron pyrite)','1 PP','Personal or Tch (+0)\\nClose (+3; LoS)','Ongoing (+0; 1 PP/h)\\nPermanent (D; +4)','Object (+0)','This spell creates a visual illusion 